column2: All other cells (i.e., excluding year, winners_rank, winners_show) are JSON strings that need to be double quoted and JSON encoded.
The year cells must be JSON numbers.  The winners_rank cells must be a JSON number or JSON null.  The winners_show cells must be JSON booleans.
Empty cells are filled in with red, and need to be filled in (i.e., TBD).
Any cell containing null is a JSON null value.
